text: Siobhan Fallon Hogan (pronounced , born May 13, 1961) is an American actress and comedian. She is known for her roles in Men in Black, Forrest Gump, The Negotiator, Holes, Daddy Day Care, Going in Style, and The House That Jack Built. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:American television writers Category:Comedians from New York City Category:Writers from New York City Category:Actors from New York City Category:Actors from Syracuse, New York Category:Writers from Syracuse, New York
